A succint summary of P, NP, NP-Complete and NP-Hard can be found here:
   https://stackoverflow.com/questions/1857244/what-are-the-differences-between-np-np-complete-and-np-hard

P:
   2-colour graph vertices
   Shortest-path
   Knapsack 0/1 

NP:
   Integer Factorization

NP-Complete:
   3SAT
   Minesweeper
   Vertex-covering
   Traveling Salesman
   Knapsack (Decision)

NP-Hard:
   Halting
   Knapsack (Optimization)


